      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Once the package has been completed, you will be able to download the file.",
      "pos": [
        11622,
        11697
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The <bpt id=\"p1\">*</bpt>.exe<ept id=\"p1\">*</ept> file that you download can be safely stored on your local computer.",
      "pos": [
        11698,
